title: #92Noon with Eric Nordquist
description:
The FAN's Eric Nordquist is in for PA today and has quite the cast of guests. First, we discuss Nordo's NFL scouting Sunday at Diamond Jo's. Resident Packer Expert, Dave Sinykin, calls in to talk the loss of his beloved team. Fox 9's, Ron Johnson, talks his own experience with the Badgers. And how he was made for GameDay. Hockey legend, Pat Micheletti, isn't mincing words about the season the Wild are having. 
Voice of the Gophers, Mike Grimm, looks back on the season so far and what this Saturday means for the Golden Gophers. And Head Coach himself, PJ Fleck, calls in to talk GameDay and the anniversary of getting the axe back.
